    <h1>Employer Hub</h1>
    <p>Emplyers can post internship opportunities and manage applications</p>
    <h2>Post A job</h2>
    <form>
        <label>Job title:</label>
        <br>
        <input type="text"></form>
        <br><br>
        <label>Location:</label>
        <br>
        <input type="text">
        <br><br>
        <label>Description</label>
        <br>
        <textarea></textarea>
        <br><br>
        <button type="submit">Post a job</button>
    </form>
    <h2>Manage Applications</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>View Applications</li>
        <li>Shortlist Candidates</li>
        <li>Reject applications</li>
    </ul>
